<p class="papertitle" align="center">Deblur a Blurred RGB Image with a Sharp NIR Image Through Local Linear Mapping</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="100%">
<p class="auther" align="center"><a href="../index.html">Tao Yue</a><sup>1</sup>, <a href="http://www.ee.washington.edu/faculty/sun/">Ming-Ting Sun</a><sup>2</sup>, <a href="http://research.microsoft.com/en-us/um/people/zhang/">Zhengyou Zhang</a><sup>3</sup>, Jinli Suo<sup>1</sup>, <a href="http://media.au.tsinghua.edu.cn/qhdai.html">Qionghai Dai</a><sup>1</sup></p>
